    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In China, wood block prints produced during the Lunar New Year as traditional domestic decoration. Prints typically summon good fortune and may also be pedagogical in nature.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
